<li><a href="http://www.wizards.com/default.asp?x=dnd/alumni/20070302a" class="external text" title="http://www.wizards.com/default.asp?x=dnd/alumni/20070302a" rel="nofollow">A Brief History of Dice</a> (in <a href="/wiki/Dungeons_%26_Dragons" title="Dungeons &amp; Dragons">Dungeons &amp; Dragons</a> games)</li>
<li><a href="http://www.thedicer.com/" class="external text" title="http://www.thedicer.com/" rel="nofollow">The Dicer</a> ‚Äì Nice virtual hexahedron dice machine.</li>
<li><a href="http://www.ambor.com/public/dice/dice.html" class="external text" title="http://www.ambor.com/public/dice/dice.html" rel="nofollow">The Dice Font</a> - Easily add dice to any of your documents</li>
</ul>
